     FAJSPP01 IF  E           K        DISK
     FMEKWP01 O   F      15            DISK                      A
     C                     SETOF                     10
     C                     Z-ADD1         MK      20
     C                     Z-ADD1         DK      20
      *
     C                     DO   *HIVAL
     C                     READ AJSPP011                 10
     C           *IN10     IFEQ '1'
     C                     GOTO ESC
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           MK        IFGT 10
     C           DK        ANDGT10
     C                     SETON                     10
     C                     GOTO ESC
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           STEP1     TAG
     C           J1MKBN    IFEQ '01'
     C                     MOVE ' '       W6      1
     C           MK        IFGT 10
     C                     GOTO ESC
     C                     ENDIF
     C           MK        ADD  1         MK
     C                     ENDIF
     C           J1MKBN    IFEQ '51'
     C                     MOVE 'D'       W6
     C           DK        IFGT 10
     C                     GOTO ESC
     C                     ENDIF
     C           DK        ADD  1         DK
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     Z-ADD1         I       10
     C                     DO   4         I
     C                     MOVE 'A'       W1      1
     C                     MOVE J1ZETI    W2      4
     C                     MOVE '001'     W3      3
     C                     Z-ADDI         W4      20
     C                     MOVE '000C'    W5      4
     C                     EXCPTDAT
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C           ESC       TAG
     C  N10                ENDDO
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
     OMEKWP01 EADD             DAT
     O                         W1         1
     O                         W2         5
     O                         W3         8
     O                         W4        10
     O                         W5        14
     O                         W6        15
